description:
views: Warn if AuraTestBase SetUp/TearDown not called

I think this code was mistakenly removed when AuraTestHelper was
introduced. It's trying to warn if someone doesn't call the base
class SetUp()/TearDown().

Arguably it's not needed in AuraTestHelper, but I don't think it
hurts to keep it there as well.

BUG=none
TEST=views_unittests

Committed: https://src.chromium.org/viewvc/chrome?view=rev&revision=196903
